&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://www.ibric.org/bric/community/popular-sori.do?mode=view&amp;amp;articleNo=9589453&amp;amp;title=%EC%83%9D%EB%AC%BC%EC%A0%95%EB%B3%B4%ED%95%99&amp;#43;%28bioinfomatics%29%EC%97%90&amp;#43;%EB%8C%80%ED%95%B4&amp;#43;%EA%B6%81%EA%B8%88%ED%95%A9%EB%8B%88%EB%8B%A4%21%21%21&amp;#43;%EB%8F%84%EC%99%80%EC%A3%BC%EC%84%B8%EC%9A%94%21%21#!/list">https://www.ibric.org/bric/community/popular-sori.do?mode=view&amp;articleNo=9589453&amp;title=%EC%83%9D%EB%AC%BC%EC%A0%95%EB%B3%B4%ED%95%99+%28bioinfomatics%29%EC%97%90+%EB%8C%80%ED%95%B4+%EA%B6%81%EA%B8%88%ED%95%A9%EB%8B%88%EB%8B%A4%21%21%21+%EB%8F%84%EC%99%80%EC%A3%BC%EC%84%B8%EC%9A%94%21%21#!/list&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
